They also published the technical specifications of the main technologies used in the operation of the system.
According to Apple and Google, the system should be deployed in three phases:
Deployment of tools to enable Governments to establish official applications to track the movement of persons infected with the coronavirus, but with data confidentiality
By integrating this function directly into iOS and Android, Google and Apple plan to solve constant surveillance problems by first implementing the system by updating the operating system and then removing it in the same way after the threat has disappeared.
